{"title":"听雨","authors":["张燕生"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":4,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"听雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张燕生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨的过程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一种从地上到天上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由天上复地上的飞跃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当雨从朴素的农谚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴落到辛勤的人们肩头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到一种奇异的脉象——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫩绿的芽儿轻舒眉眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长街开遍斗妍的花束"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄的粒儿涨满成熟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡镇飞瀑溢彩流珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘀嗒嘀嗒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘀嗒嘀嗒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗颗圆润一声声脆亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枕着山样的麦秸车听雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩虹摇动美丽的桨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小船儿推开了波浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘀嗒嘀嗒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘀嗒嘀嗒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉稳的心摆晶莹的心房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，站在敞亮的屋檐下听雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨停时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍劲的穹窿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转着一片亮丽的云霞"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}